{
  "name": "Boardtrack Era",
  "description": "1920s wooden board-track racer aesthetic. Cream/off-white enamel body, hand-painted black number circle, dark green thin pinstripes, faded brass-tone trim, and single red accent ribbon. Feels hand-built in a barn in 1923.",
